{"tid":1252709,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新選民登記】距離截止日期仲有10日 - 係剩番10日昨!!!","createTime":"2019-06-23T07:01:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T07:01:58.000Z","uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"218bdcdaf6186fd7b2401148dcf5361bd628d7b3","tid":1252709,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQXj8Ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQXj8Ad.jpg&h=cd49b3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家經歷過這兩星期的抗爭運動都辛苦了! 雖然「五大訴求」(包括埋「林鄭下台」)仍然未達到，但希望大家趁呢兩日先好好地休息，之後重新裝備再齊齊繼續抗爭吧~<br />\n<br />\n不過，有啲事就真係比較急嘅，就係 - <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">距離今屆新選民登記嘅截止日期<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>仲剩番10日咋</strong></span>!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你自己、兄弟姐妹、同事朋友等等仲未登記嘅，請好好把握今次嘅機會立即登記，以便喺<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">今年24/11嘅區議會選舉</span></ins></span> 同 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: pink;\">出年立法會選舉</span></ins></strong></span>，將一個一個賣港又冇立場嘅親共政棍跟尾狗狠狠地踢出議會，將議會嘅否決權還番俾人民吧!!!<br />\n(可惜嘅係，已登記選民嘅更改資料期限已經喺2/6結束了，但大家仍需要覆查自己嘅選民資料有冇俾人更改／刪除咗，尤其係最近換咗新身分證嘅朋友)<br />\n<br />\n有關選民登記嘅資料如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">《地方選區選民》</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaK%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=97ea38b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">《功能界別選民及／或選舉委員會界別分組選民》</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaK%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=f67c7fa6\" data-auto-link targe